## üéØ Development Paths

### For ESP8266 Development
1. Start: `PRACTICAL_EXAMPLES.md` ‚Üí ESP8266 Li-Fi Transmitter
2. Reference: `dotnet-docs/docs/iot/` ‚Üí .NET IoT patterns
3. Network: `things-network-docs/doc/content/lorawan/` ‚Üí Protocol design

### For Raspberry Pi Development
1. Start: `PRACTICAL_EXAMPLES.md` ‚Üí Raspberry Pi Li-Fi Receiver
2. Platform: `windows-iot-docs/` ‚Üí IoT platform patterns
3. Integration: `thinger-docs/` ‚Üí Device management

### For Network Architecture
1. Start: `things-network-docs/doc/content/lorawan/architecture/` ‚Üí Network design
2. Implementation: `dotnet-docs/docs/networking/` ‚Üí Network programming
3. Management: `thinger-docs/` ‚Üí Network orchestration

### For Device Management
1. Start: `thinger-docs/` ‚Üí Device provisioning patterns
2. Security: `windows-iot-docs/` ‚Üí IoT security frameworks
3. Integration: `INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md` ‚Üí Cross-platform integration

## üîÑ Maintenance
- Run `./update_docs.sh` to keep all repositories current
- Check `README.md` for detailed navigation instructions
- Review `INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md` for advanced workflows

